name: Vsekaied
description:
Vsekaied is a platformer featuring Vtubers currently in development. In this pre-alpha you'll find 2 playable levels with lots of upgrades and easter eggs.

As this game is oriented to Vtuber fans, you might be a little confused if you don't know them, but maybe you'll enjoy it as well.

The story is pretty simple: one day a group of Vtubers woke up in strange lands (maybe they got isekaied?). Now they have to use their abilities to find clues on how they got there and find a way to get back home.

Full game will feature 20+ playable Vtubers and possibly more. If you wanna help and follow the development, you can go to my patreon: Patreon

Any suggestion, bug report and constructive criticism is welcomed.
